body:
@keithmattix thanks for the heads-up. The k8s gateway that you reference exposes resource config too:
```
        resources:
          {{- toYaml .Values.global.proxy.resources | nindent 10 }}
        {{- end }}
```

The current hardcoded waypoint resources differ from `.Values.global.proxy.resources`. Should the default waypoint resource values be updated to be `Values.global.proxy.resources` or should separate values, e.g. `Values.global.waypoint.resources` be used to manage waypoint resources?

cc: @howardjohn
